Create symlink to the destination /windows/Dropbox from the created file Dropbox (Maestral)
ln -s /windows/Dropbox "Dropbox (Maestral)"

Limit journal log space: 
sudo vim /etc/systemd/journald.conf
SystemMaxUse=50M
